        "Avoid aminoglycoside monotherapy.",
        "Monotherapy selected on the basis of in vitro susceptibility test results is as efficacious as combination therapy.",
        "IDSA Guidelines recommend combination therapy for pneumonia caused by Pseudomonas aeruginosa in patients who are in septic shock or have risk factors for high mortality (weak recommendation, very low quality evidence).",
